== Overview ==
The Anomaly Detector is another [[:Category:Modules (Utility)|passive module]]. It allows squads to detect anomalous features in the surrounding terrain such as [[Firewells]] and [[Bases]] with more ease.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Anomaly Detector can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
